skdetail:

Invocation Name: high low game
des: Guess a number, and Alexa will tell you if you need to guess higher or lower. After guessing the number, she will also tell you how many tries it took you to guess the number. See if you can guess in five tries or less! For the little ones that need help, Alexa can provide additional clues too!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
